      about building beautiful experiences on the web. I sometimes also do some freelance
      work on the side, such as for <Anchor
        href=""
        img="preview-wth"
        imgAlt="Screenshot of WTH 2021 website"
        client:only="svelte">WTH 2021</Anchor
